<TITLE> Child killed in road accident in Bagerhat </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Bagerhat, May 28 (bdnews24.com)  A road accident in Bagerhat left a child dead and his father injured on Friday. The child has been identified as Zahirul Islam, 10. His father, Md Zafar, 40, has been admitted to Bagerhat Sadr Hospital. Bagerhat Sadr police's sub-inspector Shahidul Islam told bdnews24.com that the accident occurred at about 9 am when a Dhaka-bound commuter bus collided head-on with a motorcycle carrying Zahir and his father. Zahir died on the spot, the police officer said, and his body has been sent to the Bagerhat Sadr Hospital for an autopsy. Police, however, could not arrest the bus driver, Islam added. bdnews
